sources.title: 1934 Herz Ist Trumpf ( Jenny Jugo, Paul Hörbiger)
sources.description: Film aus dem deutschen dritten Reich von 1934. Herz ist Trumpf. u.a mit Jenny Jugo und Paul Hörbiger

metadata.Plot: Hotel tycoon Paulsen re-meets an old flame who mistakes him for a waiter. Paulsen's daughter Toni likes hotelier Reno and accepts to work for him as a waitress and chambermaid because she wants to be loved for herself, not her money.
metadata.Writer: Eduard Andrés, Harald G. Petersson, Walter Wassermann
metadata.Actors: Jenny Jugo, Paul Hörbiger, Friedrich Benfer
